name.description: The name of property, in camelCase

index.description: To define property like a index

indexFields.description: Fields to do composite unique index

indexName.description: The name of index, if there are various indexes with the same name, they will be grouped

indexUsing.description: To define property like a index

isI18n.description: Set property as i18n, this property will be used to translate the entity in the translation table

example.description: Example value for property, this value will be used in swagger documentation

decimals.description: Total digits of the number and length of the decimal places in the back of the number, example: [10, 2].

autoIncrement.description: Set number property as auto increment

applyTimezone.description: Apply timezone to date property, by default is true

resolverType.description: Type of resolver, query or mutation

singularName.description: Singular name of the property referred to in the relationship, only for one-to-many and many-to-many relationship, example: book

aggregateName.description: Aggregate referring to this relationship, example: LibraryAuthor

modulePath.description: Path to the module that refers to this relationship, example: library/author

key.description: Property key that refers to this relationship, only for many-to-one relationship, example: id

field.description: Field to obtain the relationship data, example: author

description.description: The description of the relationship field

avoidConstraint.description: Avoid constraint rules for this relationship

packageName.description: Path to packageName where is the relationship, example: @aurora-ts/core

isDenormalized.description: Set many-to-many relationship as denormalized, creating a field to store the selected ids

webComponentDefinition.description: Web Component that wil be rendered for this property

detailSort.description: Web component order on detail view

isDetailHidden.description: Set hidden web component on detail view

listSort.description: Web component order on list view

isListHidden.description: Set hidden web component on list view

excludedOperationDefinition.description: Operations to be excluded from the module

outlineFontSetIcon.description: Font set outline icon to be used in the front application

outlineIcon.description: Outline icon to be used in the front application

solidFontSetIcon.description: Font set solid icon to be used in the front application

solidIcon.description: Solid icon to be used in the front application

pivotTableDefinition.description: Relationship pivot table definition for this relationship

boundedContextName.description: The name of the package, singular in kebab-case

moduleName.description: The name of the module, singular in kebab-case

moduleNames.description: The name of the module, plural in kebab-case

aggregateName.description: The name of the aggregateName, singular in PascalCase

hasOAuth.description: Enabled authentication for this pivot table

schema.description: Make agile applications without technical debt

boundedContextName.description: The name of the package, singular in kebab case

moduleName.description: The name of the module, singular in kebab case

moduleNames.description: The name of the module, plural in kebab case

aggregateName.description: The name of the aggregateName, singular in pascal case, is composed of the boundedContextName plus the moduleName

excludedFiles.description: Files to be excluded from the module

schema.title: Aurora Agile Meta Framework
